name: Jurassic Pinball
overview: The most entertaining Pinball is back! Enjoy Jurassic Pinball, a perfect reproduction of a real pinball machine, with all the graphic details and sounds. Discover all the secrets, complete all the missions and become number 1 in the world or the best among your Friends, posting your high score on the online leaderboard. • Arcade design. • Set in the Jurassic age. • Multiball, Extraball, Skillshot, Jackpots... • Reproduction with all the details, lights and sounds. • 4 different cameras to choose from. • Online Leaderboard.
